>Description:
I don't much care for the "comment"/"uncomment"
menu entries.  It would be so much nicer if we could
stuff the selected text in a box, which DrScheme
then knows to treat as a comment.  Then uncommenting
doesn't need to putz with deleting semi-colons, and
users can maybe collapse a comment box also.
