 There are no "comment boxes" at the moment, and I think that the
 toughest part of this request is figuring out how to make comment boxes
 that look different from the other boxes in a clear, suggestive way.
 
 I guess we could get rid of the old "text" boxes, by changing their
 meaning.
 
